#. <section class="sutta" id="sn54.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn54.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 54"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 54"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Ekadhammavagga"
msgstr "1. One Thing"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 3. Suddhikasutta → suddhakasuttaṃ (bj) | suddhakaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn54.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Suddhikasutta"
msgstr "3. Plain Version"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.3:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ānāpānassati, bhikkhave, bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti mahānisaṃsā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when mindfulness of breathing is developed and cultivated it’s "
"very fruitful and beneficial."

msgctxt "sn54.3:1.2"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvitā ca, bhikkhave, ānāpānassati kathaṃ bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti "
"mahānisaṃsā?"
msgstr ""
"And how is mindfulness of breathing developed and cultivated to be very "
"fruitful and beneficial?"

msgctxt "sn54.3:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu araññagato vā rukkhamūlagato vā suññāgāragato vā "
"nisīdati pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ "
"upaṭṭhapetvā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant has gone to a wilderness, or to the root of a tree, or "
"to an empty hut. They sit down cross-legged, with their body straight, and "
"establish mindfulness right there."

msgctxt "sn54.3:1.4"
msgid "So satova assasati, satova passasati … pe …"
msgstr "Just mindful, they breathe in. Mindful, they breathe out. …"

msgctxt "sn54.3:1.5"
msgid ""
"‘paṭinissaggānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘paṭinissaggānupassī "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati."
msgstr ""
"They practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe in observing letting go.’ They "
"practice like this: ‘I’ll breathe out observing letting go.’"

msgctxt "sn54.3:1.6"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvitā kho, bhikkhave, ānāpānassati evaṃ bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti "
"mahānisaṃsā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Mindfulness of breathing, when developed and cultivated in this way, is very "
"fruitful and beneficial.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn54.3:1.7"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
